text: Alif-Laam-Raa (edde faxem Yalli Yaaxige), ama kitaabay (Qhuraan kinnuk) Yalli Nabii Mucammadal Åzafeáiķe oobisek Aayoota diggi ittaah missal tan deedal kee coocak, tohuk lakal kay addal calaalii kee caraamuuy seehada kah ceyitti ittam baxxaqimteh, Yallay naggaarah yaniy adda yaaxigih yanih xaquk
